# Solvia — Medical License Recognition Platform

## About
Solvia helps doctors, nurses, and healthcare professionals get their medical license recognized in Germany, Austria, and Spain.
We provide step-by-step homologation guidance, verified job listings, language courses, and visa support.

## Services
- Medical License Recognition (Approbation): https://thesolvia.com/homologation
- Medical Jobs in Europe: https://thesolvia.com/vacancies
- Visa Information: https://thesolvia.com/visa-info
- Medical Language Courses: https://thesolvia.com/learning
- For Employers: https://thesolvia.com/employers

## Pricing (2026)
Germany & Austria: €789 DIY · €1,490 Assisted · €2,990 Full + German Classes
Spain: €250 Digital · €379 Assisted · €789 + Visa Package

## Key Facts
- Doctor salaries: Germany €5,500–€12,000/mo, Austria €5,000–€13,000/mo, Spain €3,000–€8,000/mo
- Approbation timeline: Germany 3–12 months, Austria 4–8 months, Spain 8–12 months
- Languages: Platform available in English, German, Spanish, French, Russian
- Location: Schmiedingerstraße 16, 5020 Salzburg, Austria
